# changes to allow two DES cores to be selected for different ARM variants.
#
# Revision 1.28  1998/06/10 22:50:12  timc
# Robert Au added for PPC targets
# CVS:
# CVS:
#
# Revision 1.27  1998/06/09 22:21:56  remi
